{"tid":691694,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Facebook承認與華為等中國科技公司分享數據","createTime":"2018-06-06T03:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-06T06:28:24.000Z","uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d89c448fd4c0562712694b2ec52c2c6c776f1b1f","tid":691694,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/fin/20180606/s00010/3ec4847de9b5f9f8507db3af5781c23f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2F20180606%2Fs00010%2F3ec4847de9b5f9f8507db3af5781c23f.jpg&h=4a05c500&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2018年6月6日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》報道，Facebook與至少四家中國科技公司有數據共享協議，而該協議可追溯至2010年。根據協議內容，Facebook允許華為、聯想、廣東歐珀移動通信和TCL集團訪問設備用戶及其朋友的詳細信息。但Facebook表示，可能於本周結束與華為的協議。<br />\n<br />\n美國情報機構警告，華為與中國政府關係密切，可能對國家安全構成威脅，惟Facebook指，Facebook的用戶數據並沒有儲存在華為的服務器上。<br />\n<br />\n報道又指，Facebook與逾60家公司有數據共享協議，當中包括蘋果公司和亞馬遜公司。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook用戶私隱問題已惹來市場關注。蘋果早前在全球開發大會(WWDC)上宣布，之後推出新iOS和Mac作業系統版本時，會嘗試阻截Facebook自動追蹤網絡用戶的工具。"},{"pid":"81e1f792e7688ac338d63b669d6c9312e23897a6","tid":691694,"uid":14103,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:44:10.000Z","msg":"一向都知佢奶共想打入支那市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a933fe3e2782b9534641e7ca8ab89311f9199f","tid":691694,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c3f17c606d87610308b2dfebf41e588ef465c69","tid":691694,"uid":11703,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T03:57:11.000Z","msg":"所以成日都話愈支持所謂多元化嘅人就愈貪錢同奶共<br />\n一個係佢<br />\n一個係Gay Cook"},{"pid":"66e66fdb79d14fd4f1f2f08a59bf0e044303f2f7","tid":691694,"uid":51129,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-06T04:00:59.000Z","msg":"facebook<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmo